            "title": "欧洲股市早段上升\r\n",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">      欧洲股市早段上升。英国富时100指数报8,666.19点，升3.22点(0.04%)；德国DAX指数报22,330.26点，升15.61点(0.07%)；法国CAC 40指数报8,149.03点，升26.45点(0.33%)。 <br/> (WL)</span>\n</div>",
